data.description: Four bedroom 3 bath house in Ashville!  This low maintenance vinyl siding home is located on approx. 2 acres. This well loved home features hardwood floors throughout the living room, dining room and kitchen. Spacious kitchen offers a triple bowl gourmet sink, island, and a pantry. This 2500+/- square foot home has two master bedrooms or one could be used as an in-law suite, extra den or family room if preferred. There are two laundry rooms. One located on each side of the home. You will have plenty of room to spread out here!  Outside you will enjoy the covered front porch, new back deck, and flat yard for outdoor activities!  There is approximately 1 acre fenced away from the home. The detached garage has electricity and offers all kinds of possibilities!
